long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Manage and analyze Speed Kit directly from your browser!
 
TURN SPEED KIT ON/OFF
Turning Speed Kit on and off only affects the selected domain in your browser. Other users and browsers remain unaffected.
 
UPDATE YOUR CONTENT
A page of your website contains outdated content? Simply click on "Update This Page" to refresh the selected page.
 
OVERALL STATUS
The Overall Status shows if Speed Kit is activated for general website visitors.
 
CONTENT SERVED
Content Served indicates whether the content on your currently opened page is served “via Speed Kit” or “without Speed Kit”.
